msgid ""
"IsAlgo is your go-to source for expertly crafted trading strategies designed"
" specifically for the"
msgstr "IsAlgo は、特別に設計された、専門的に作成された取引戦略の頼りになる情報源です。"

msgid ""
"platform, it also provides automation solutions to streamline your trading "
